VERTICAL = "DECREASED LEVEL OF UP AND DOWN BASED FROM LOGIC VALUES GIVEN OFF OF THE LOGIC OF A SPATIAL POINT INSIDE TIME ALLOWING A HORIZONTAL EFFECT TO FOLLOW AN EXISTENCE EXISTING PARTICLE INSIDE AND OUTSIDE TIME GIVING EXISTENCE TO A MACRO VERTICLE EFFECT WITH TRUE LOGIC OF TRUTH INFORMATION GIVING PERMISSION TO CREATE AND DEVELOP A SPECIFIC CREATOR FREQUENCY WITHIN CHOSEN CREATORS AND MAY ACKNOWLEDGE FOR THE FIRST TIME" 
